Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:09.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:20.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.52,0:00:39.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.76,0:00:46.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.00,0:00:54.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.34,0:00:59.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.78,0:01:07.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.22,0:01:14.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.53,0:01:20.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.23,0:01:28.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.52,0:01:38.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am Wauf, the captain of the Messis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.65,0:01:45.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,The highland aerial base, found on\Na Chor Tempest scouting flight...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.19,0:01:47.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,...has since vanished without a trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.26,0:01:52.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Four of Chor Tempest's Simouns\Nhave already left the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.00,0:01:57.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,The sharp surge in enemy attacks\Nthe last 12 hours is worrisome.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:02:02.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Messis has been left with\Nonly two Simouns on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.61,0:02:05.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm getting a bad feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.51,0:02:06.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.11,0:02:08.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone's in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.45,0:02:11.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,The kitchen staff\Ncan be relieved for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:13.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.90,0:02:34.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.19,0:02:49.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.62,0:02:52.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:02:56.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,He sure does have\Na screwed-up face.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:02:59.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,You think he takes after his owner?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:01.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roatreamon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:04.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Or maybe the one who made him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:12.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,How can you laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:13.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:21.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,A-Aircraft sighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:23.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:25.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nine o'clock! A fleet of planes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:26.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Non-Simoun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:30.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nine o'clock!\NA fleet of planes! Non-Simoun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.33,0:03:32.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,We should assume\Nthey've spotted us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:35.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Six o'clock! A fleet of planes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:36.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Take us down lower!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:39.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Any lower and we'll hit trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.27,0:03:42.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter! Mow them down!\NFind a hiding place for this ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:51.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's a hill at one o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.42,0:03:54.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Turn us around at full speed!\NPrepare to land!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.06,0:04:02.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can fight with two Simouns,\Nbut it's over if the Messis falls!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:06.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Baby birds who've lost their mother\Nare doomed to starve to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:09.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't say things like that.\NYou'll frighten the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:12.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:15.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone's not scared at all, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.08,0:04:27.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on. Let's go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:33.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:41.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simouns are the vehicles\Nof the gods... They can't fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.68,0:04:59.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,What should we do, Dominüra?\NPursue the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:00.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:04.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,The priority now is\Nto protect the Messis.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:07.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll flank and keep\Nits launch position undetected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:11.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Good idea. We'll attack by land,\Nusing it as a smokescreen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:12.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.47,0:05:15.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,You know what, Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:16.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:20.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,I kind of brought Roatreamon's\Nstuffed animal with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.14,0:05:54.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Drop anchor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:56.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now dropping anchor!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:57.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Captain, I believe we're\Ngoing to get away with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:06:59.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:03.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,So we pulled the wool\Nover their eyes after all, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:10.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,It seems they're gone. Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:11.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:22.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,They made it look like they'd gone,\Nbut they were keeping an eye out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:25.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Should we head back now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:27.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:31.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have no idea how to survive here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.44,0:07:37.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Having honed our war skills\Nisn't anything to brag about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.21,0:07:40.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,War skills, did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:43.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's my war skills...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:50.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Techniques for survival...\NI've got to learn more about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:04.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's quiet here, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.41,0:08:10.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:14.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,You said you'd do it for me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.08,0:08:18.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.05,0:08:24.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,I never intended to put\Nsuch a burden on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:29.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's just that unless I know\NI'm doing it for someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:33.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the way I am right now,\NI have no chance of moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:48.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:52.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,I do understand\Nhow you feel, Dominüra.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:58.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I don't understand\Nwhy I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:05.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because you're my pair... That's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:17.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,We should've realized it sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:21.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,So you're saying\Nthe others were lured away?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:24.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NThey've splintered Chor Tempest...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:26.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,...forcing it\Nto disperse its combat power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.12,0:09:31.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's going to be all right, Rimone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:35.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,They still haven't\Npinpointed our exact location.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:36.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:40.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you're\Nas aware of this as I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:43.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,The sun will rise soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:47.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Once the enemy attacks again,\Nthere'll be no escaping detection.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:51.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,In that case, what kind\Nof choices do we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:55.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,One would be to wait for\Nthe four Simouns' return...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:10:00.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and sit tight until we can launch\Na counterattack against the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:01.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,The other would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:05.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,...to make our escape from\Nthis airspace as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:10.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then what will become\Nof Neviril and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:11.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.76,0:10:14.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is your opinion, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:19.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,As things stand, the survival rate for\Nthe Simouns that have yet to return...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:23.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,...is extremely low.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:25.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,How can you utter\Nsuch groundless rubbish?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.78,0:10:29.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest is Kyuukoku's\Nfinest chor! We can't fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:31.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:34.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're all coming back for sure.\NSo try to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:38.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:42.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll search for the Simouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.13,0:10:43.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,What about the Messis?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:47.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,The captain's view about Shoukoku's\Nnew aircraft attacking again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.03,0:10:49.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,...isn't guaranteed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:52.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Your behavior is quite violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.64,0:10:53.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:56.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want you to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.81,0:10:57.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,You and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:10:59.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone is my pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.61,0:11:02.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.31,0:11:04.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I am Rimone's pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:14.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:21.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's going on with you? All of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:24.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,How can you stay so calm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:28.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,When your own\Ncomrades are in peril?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:32.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,I could never bring myself\Nto abandon my comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:36.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don't mean comrades.\NYou mean Neviril, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.28,0:11:39.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Since when is Neviril your underling?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:41.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,My underling?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.12,0:11:45.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea is\NChor Tempest's highest sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:47.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thinking someone\Nlike you can protect her...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:49.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,...is gross arrogance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:56.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:11:59.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:09.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone, you and I will go with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.48,0:12:13.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,But give me a little time\Nbefore we leave. I won't be long.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:18.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Besides, in the state\Nyou're in right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.19,0:12:22.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,...you can't activate the Simoun\Nwith Aer, can you, Paraietta?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:48.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominüra!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:51.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see someone else got here first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:57.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Without something to believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:13:01.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,...none of us can even\Nplant our feet on the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:06.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,In my case, that was Kyuukoku,\Nas well as Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:15.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:21.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simouns taught me something...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.89,0:13:24.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Something I never wanted to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:27.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please tell me...\NWhat was it that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:31.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,What on earth did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.06,0:13:34.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Forget about that day, Waporif.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.07,0:13:35.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.07,0:13:39.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's the last warning\NI'll be giving you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:51.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,As we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:53.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:56.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Planes sighted at eight o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:14:00.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,They got here sooner than I thought.\NWe probably don't have time to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:06.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Messis will remain moored\Nhere and attempt a counterattack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:09.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:11.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:13.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want you, Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:17.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because unless you come\Nwith me, I can't save Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:23.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:26.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.89,0:14:28.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:31.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.96,0:14:35.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,I forgot to give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:52.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:14:54.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're flying so high!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.35,0:14:56.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're practically Simouns!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.60,0:15:13.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra! Rimone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.40,0:15:17.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer, let's go! The Falcon Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:29.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer! The Falcon\NRi Majon one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.85,0:15:32.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right! As many times as it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:41.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone, which Ri Majon can we do\Nthat has the most destructive power?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.43,0:15:44.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Wave Crest Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.05,0:16:08.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone! One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.12,0:16:10.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wave Crest Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:15.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:18.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:22.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,They've made huge technological\Nadvances in such a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.30,0:16:26.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,They haven't reached the Simouns'\Nlevel yet, but such great numbers...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.64,0:16:29.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Fish Silhouette Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:36.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's no good! We can't do\NRi Majons with all this interference!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.32,0:16:40.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Messis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:48.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.96,0:16:51.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Has the time come for us to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:56.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.37,0:16:57.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.47,0:17:00.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, not me. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:03.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're afraid, aren't you, Dominüra?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.91,0:17:08.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who ever thought you'd\Nunderstand me to that degree?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:12.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I saw that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:14.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was a terrifying sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:22.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,It destroyed every last shred of my\Npride and shattered all I believed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:25.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,But that's not what I'm afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:30.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Beyond that terrible sight,\NI caught a glimpse of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.74,0:17:32.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.67,0:17:34.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:39.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't describe it in words.\NBut if I had to give it a name...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.11,0:17:41.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'd call it hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:45.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,For the Messis...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:48.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're fighting so\Nthat we might be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.22,0:17:51.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're fighting for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.19,0:17:53.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.36,0:17:58.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't let the sibyllae's\Nprayers be in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:18:03.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll draw the enemy's attention\Nso the priestesses can escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.40,0:18:04.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.78,0:18:12.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.08,0:18:15.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Madness! Are they trying to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.35,0:18:17.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are they doing it for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:19.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm sure they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.99,0:18:27.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Prepare the cannons!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:31.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.70,0:18:32.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:35.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:37.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter what may lie ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.90,0:18:40.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:47.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess we lost sight of them, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:48.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.05,0:18:54.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is this? This feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:58.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,It feels so familiar\Nyet so relentlessly cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:18:59.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:01.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Over there... Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.96,0:19:06.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:08.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:21.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.75,0:19:23.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Dominüra! Rimone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.38,0:19:26.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,You've got to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.42,0:19:27.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's the Emerald...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.96,0:19:33.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.29,0:19:36.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hold up, who's doing\Nthe Emerald Ri Majon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:40.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,I never thought\Nwe'd ever see it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:43.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're heading right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.37,0:19:44.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're sure? That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.04,0:19:47.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,No! They'll be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:50.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Stop it... please...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.88,0:19:55.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.69,0:20:03.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:06.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:08.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm not afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.86,0:20:11.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, I'm not afraid either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:15.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.93,0:20:17.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Together...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:21.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Forever and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.21,0:20:23.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, forever and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:20:57.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nothing's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.08,0:21:03.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait. Where did\NDominüra and Rimone go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.85,0:21:05.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:10.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,They don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.87,0:21:21.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:23.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Captain! It's the Simouns!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.24,0:21:26.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness! They're all safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.27,0:21:30.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.25,0:21:35.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.31,0:21:36.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:37.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's going on?\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.78,0:21:39.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,C-Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.75,0:21:42.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Directly overhead...\NI-It's the Arcus Prima!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.63,0:21:55.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was a close shave,\Nbut it seems we're in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:58.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sorry to have kept\Nyou waiting, my sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.97,0:22:02.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everybody...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.81,0:22:11.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am Wauf, the captain of the Messis.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:14.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,In the end, we survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.85,0:22:19.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thanks to the Arcus Prima and the\Nreturn of Chor Tempest's Simouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.29,0:22:28.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,But as for the Simoun flown by Sibylla\NDominüra and Sibylla Rimone...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.50,0:22:31.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,We never found\Neven the slightest trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.38,0:22:48.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.12,0:22:52.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.36,0:22:59.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.40,0:23:07.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.78,0:23:19.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,"I want to get closer to you."\N"I want to feel your pulse."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.92,0:23:24.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.09,0:23:28.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.09,0:23:32.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.06,0:23:38.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.97,0:23:44.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the sky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.51,0:23:47.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.91,0:23:53.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.62,0:23:59.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.43,0:24:06.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.33,0:24:12.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Headed for the forbidden land, Chor\NTempest makes a startling discovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.97,0:24:15.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.71,0:24:16.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Ruins
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.88,0:24:18.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Ruins\NThe Ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.21,0:24:20.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Ruins
